    "bio": "Influencers.club is an Influencer marketing platform focused on creator data APIs. \n\nWe allow companies in any industry to build automated creator workflows from discovery to enrichment to power influencer acquisition, partnership automation, and custom solutions with social data, emails, full social graph across all social platforms, analytics, demographics and 200+ insights.",
